snippet: What would the composer Jerome Kern have made of Woodstock? That question was asked but not answered on Saturday evening at the 92nd Street Y.
abstract: Stephen Holden reviews concert tribute to popular music composer Jerome Kern entitled The Song Is You, featuring large cast of performers, at 92nd Street Y as part of its Lyrics and Lyricists series.
lead_paragraph: What would the composer Jerome Kern have made of Woodstock? That question was asked but not answered on Saturday evening at the 92nd Street Y.

headline.seo: ‘Jerome Kern: The Song Is You’ at the 92nd Street Y
